data.name: Any% All Keys
data.rules:
Beat the Game with these Goals: 
• Player must collect All Keys and then beat K. Rool from a fresh file

Restriction and Clarifications: 
• In-game cheats are ALLOWED
• Acquiring Key 5 from Aztec is ALLOWED
• Freeing K. Lumsy is not required
